Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:11.05,Black Lagoon Omake Normal,Normal,0000,0000,0000,,Radical Revy-chan kính chào quí khán giả!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:13.77,Black Lagoon Omake Normal,Normal,0000,0000,0000,,Ai đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:17.77,Black Lagoon Omake Normal,Normal,0000,0000,0000,,~ Cô Gái Phép Thuật ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:17.83,Copy of Black Lagoon Omake Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(496,326)}A4VF Present
